{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d40238593","title":"毛泽东对《无产阶级专政胜利万岁》一稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"36d32eee27","index":0,"year":1971,"month":3,"day":15,"articleId":"4d40238593","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第26册 “文化大革命”参考资料 中册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5b064fbdca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东对《无产阶级专政胜利万岁》一稿的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"499734ad0d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七一年三月十五日）看了一遍，觉得可用","index":1,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f245b0ee2","type":"paragraph","text":"只在十八页上去掉一个词，以便突出马列。十七页上已有了这个词也就够了。我党多年来不读马、列，不突出马、列，竞让一些骗子骗了多年，使很多人甚至不知道什么是唯物论，什么是唯心论。在庐山闹出大笑话。这个教训非常严重，这几年应当特别注意宣传马、列，","index":2,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a28c0f0034","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十五日九时毛泽东在一个材料上的批示","index":3,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a85a3a3fde","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七一年三月三十日）","index":4,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6a248b6a3","type":"paragraph","text":"此件留待军委办事组各同志一阅。上了陈伯达赋船，年深日久，虽有庐山以来半年的时问，经过各种批判会议，到三月十儿才讲出几句真话，真是上贼船容易下赋船难。人一输了理（就是走错了路线），就怕揭，庐山会议上的那种狂进攻的勇气，不知跑到那里去了。","index":5,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c0c425c023","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07de9f4778","type":"paragraph","text":"三月玉十日","index":7,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf40322a3b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席在最后一页批示这还只是中明。下文如何，要看行动。","index":8,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"4d40238593","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":533,"end":533}}}},"__N_SSG":true}